The paper deals with the optimization of joint source, channel, and space-time coding in a MIMO system, which involves information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG) concepts. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
